            <p id="category-description">Hatchbacks are cars with an upward swinging rear door. They are built primarily to serve the dual function of being a passenger car and a mini-cargo car. This car classification features a three-box category. Hatchbacks have great fuel economy, high ground clearance and sleek interior. They are the perfect car for families.</p>
